room_title: Escape room "Dragon Tower VR" by Time Travel Escapes in West Palm Beach
room_description: A small seaside town, an evil alchemist and a hungry dragon. Hardly the place for a few hapless time travelers! Accused of a crime you did not commit, you must find a way to ESCAPE your prison before you meet your fiery fate! Can you ESCAPE the Dragon Tower before the clock strikes 6 when the dragons return for their annual sacrifice?
